  "finalSubmissionGuidelines": "<p>Since the requirements are loose you should take extra time to showcase your features in a video and maybe a second one with a code walk through. &nbsp; If you want to showcase your solution on the challenge view too you are welcome but this is not required. &nbsp; Here are the key factors we are looking for: &nbsp;1.) &nbsp;Small footprint on data model. &nbsp;2.) easy and unobtrusive to use. 3.) flexible so we can add it in new components. &nbsp; Please include your src in a zip file and a well articulated deployment guide. &nbsp; A pull request is optional but not required.</p>\n",
